rows.label: tlk45500153_07_msg0001
rows.name:
Let me tell you about something that
happened while I was at the baths.

rows.label: tlk45500153_07_msg0002
rows.name:
I was just getting ready for a nice soak,
chatting about the latest gossip, when
an earthquake shook the whole place!

rows.label: tlk45500153_07_msg0003
rows.name:
Ran out onto the roof stark naked I did,
and what do you think I saw? Only the
World Tree drawing closer and closer!

rows.label: tlk45500153_07_msg0004
rows.name:
And that wasn't the end of it, either!
Suddenly the Divine Beast itself unleashed
a mighty attack!

rows.label: tlk45500153_07_msg0005
rows.name:
It blew up such a powerful wind,
my towel was swept clean away!

rows.label: tlk45500153_07_msg0006
rows.name:
Everyone scrambled back down
into the baths as fast as our
legs could carry us!
